* Ray Liotta as Vincent , Meemaw 's bookie .
* Jason Kravits as Dr. Ronald Hodges , a NASA engineer and college roommate of Mr. Givens .
He makes a presentation about his work to Mr. Givens ' science class , which intrigues Sheldon to solve the challenges of reusable launch systems .
