Section::::Reception .
Section::::Critical reception .
The review aggregator website Rotten Tomatoes reported a 76 % approval rating with an average rating of 6.81/10 based on 41 reviews .
The website 's consensus reads , " Young Sheldons appealing cast and relatable themes bring a freshand overall enjoyableperspective to its central character 's familiar story .
"
Metacritic , which uses a weighted average , assigned a score of 63 out of 100 based on 25 critics , indicating " generally favorable reviews " .
